## Development

```bash
# Install dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/

# Lint
ruff check .

# Type check
mypy devrecai/

# Run TUI in dev mode (Textual console)
textual run --dev devrecai/tui/app.py
```

